[
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Metropolis算法简要证明",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            69,
            474,
            837,
            620
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Metropolis算法",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            144,
            410,
            242
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "目的：从 $f(x)$ 中抽取样本",
        "bbox": [
            91,
            329,
            501,
            414
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法：用迭代算法生成随机变量序列（马尔可夫链）",
        "bbox": [
            83,
            512,
            936,
            592
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "要求：建议分布需要对称",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            696,
            502,
            772
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "步骤 ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            142,
            196,
            233
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "1. 给定 $x^{t - 1}$ , 从建议分布 $J(x^{t} \\mid x^{t - 1})$ 中抽取样本, 并记为 $x^{*}$ ",
            "2. 计算 $r = \\frac{f(x^{*})}{f(x^{t - 1})}$ , 并从 $U[0,1]$ 中抽取 $u$ ",
            "3. 若 $u \\leq \\min \\{r, 1\\}$ , 则令 $x^{t} = x^{*}$ ; 否则令 $x^{t} = x^{t - 1}$ "
        ],
        "bbox": [
            83,
            320,
            893,
            740
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "问题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            98,
            148,
            196,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "1. 按以上方法得到的随机变量序列收敛，即存在平稳分布。（此问题由随机过程可证。）",
            "2. 平稳分布为 $f$ , 即随机变量序列的平稳分布为目标分布。"
        ],
        "bbox": [
            83,
            329,
            901,
            890
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "记号",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            146,
            195,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "- 马尔科夫链（Markov chain）： $X_{1}, X_{2}, \\ldots, X_{t}, X_{t+1}, \\ldots$ ",
            "- 转移函数（transition kernel）："
        ],
        "bbox": [
            84,
            296,
            764,
            472
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nT (b | a) \\doteq P (X _ {t + 1} = b | X _ {t} = a) \\doteq f _ {X _ {t + 1} | X _ {t}} (b | a)\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            226,
            531,
            758,
            600
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "从 $X_{t} = a$ 转移到 $X_{t + 1} = b$ 的概率, 或",
            "$\\bullet$ 给定 $X_{t} = a$ 时 $X_{t + 1} = b$ 的条件密度"
        ],
        "bbox": [
            101,
            644,
            595,
            825
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "定义",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            142,
            196,
            237
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "若 $T$ 对某一（密度）函数 $f$ 满足：对任意 $a$ 和 $b$ ，有",
        "bbox": [
            83,
            318,
            712,
            387
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nT (b | a) \\times f (a) = T (a | b) \\times f (b),\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            287,
            466,
            694,
            535
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则称 $T$ 满足平衡条件（detailed balanced condition）。",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            614,
            740,
            674
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "引理",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            146,
            200,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "对于马尔科夫链 $X_{1}, X_{2}, \\ldots, X_{t}, X_{t+1}, \\ldots$ , $T$ 为该马尔科夫链的转移函数。若 $T$ 满足平衡条件（detailed balanced condition），则对应的密度函数 $f$ 为该马氏链的平稳分布。",
        "bbox": [
            83,
            316,
            913,
            637
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "证明",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            146,
            194,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "设 $X_{t}$ 的密度函数为 $f_{X_{t}}$ 。对任意 $a$ 和 $b$ , 有",
        "bbox": [
            85,
            327,
            595,
            396
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} f _ {X _ {t + 1}, X _ {t}} (b, a) = f _ {X _ {t + 1} | X _ {t}} (b | a) \\times f _ {X _ {t}} (a) \\doteq T (b | a) \\times f _ {X _ {t}} (a) \\\\ = T (a | b) \\times f _ {X _ {t}} (b) \\doteq f _ {X _ {t + 1} | X _ {t}} (a | b) \\times f _ {X _ {t}} (b) = f _ {X _ {t + 1}, X _ {t}} (a, b) 。 \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            123,
            481,
            861,
            696
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "证明",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            146,
            194,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} f _ {X _ {t + 1}} (b) = \\int f _ {X _ {t + 1}, X _ {t}} (b, a) d a = \\int f _ {X _ {t + 1}, X _ {t}} (a, b) d a \\\\ = \\int f _ {X _ {t + 1} | X _ {t}} (a | b) \\times f _ {X _ {t}} (b) d a = f _ {X _ {t}} (b) \\times \\int f _ {X _ {t + 1} | X _ {t}} (a | b) d a = f _ {X _ {t}} (b) \\circ \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            94,
            303,
            889,
            588
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "可见 $f_{X_{t + 1}}(b) = f_{X_t}(b)$ 对任意 $b$ 成立，即 $X_{t + 1}$ 的密度函数仍为 $f_{X_t}$ ，故 $f_{X_t}$ 为平稳分布。",
        "bbox": [
            83,
            655,
            908,
            801
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "定理",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            148,
            195,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Metropolis算法所提出的 $T$ 满足密度函数为目标分布 $f$ 的平衡条件。",
        "bbox": [
            83,
            320,
            912,
            540
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "证明",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            146,
            194,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "对任意 $a$ 和 $b$ , 有",
        "bbox": [
            83,
            320,
            300,
            379
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} T (b | a) \\times f (a) = J (b | a) \\times \\min \\{r, 1 \\} \\times f (a) \\\\ = J (b | a) \\times \\min \\left\\{\\frac {f (b)}{f (a)}, 1 \\right\\} \\times f (a) = J (b | a) \\times \\min \\{f (b), f (a) \\}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            464,
            881,
            792
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "证明",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            146,
            194,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} T (a | b) \\times f (b) = J (a | b) \\times \\min  \\{r, 1 \\} \\times f (b) \\\\ = J (a | b) \\times \\min \\left\\{\\frac {f (a)}{f (b)}, 1 \\right\\} \\times f (b) = J (a | b) \\times \\min \\{f (a), f (b) \\}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            318,
            881,
            646
        ],
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "证明",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            146,
            194,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 12
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "- $T(b \\mid a) \\times f(a) = J(b \\mid a) \\times \\min \\{f(b), f(a)\\}$ ; ",
            "$T(a|b) \\times f(b) = J(a|b) \\times \\min \\{f(a), f(b)\\}$ ; ",
            "$\\cdot J(b \\mid a) = J(a \\mid b)$ ; ",
            "- $T(b \\mid a) \\times f(a) = T(a \\mid b) \\times f(b)$ （满足平衡条件）"
        ],
        "bbox": [
            84,
            312,
            740,
            803
        ],
        "page_idx": 12
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "注 ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            148,
            147,
            231
        ],
        "page_idx": 13
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "$\\bullet$ Metropolis算法中要求 $J(b \\mid a) = J(a \\mid b)$ , 即建议分布为对称。 ",
            "- Metropolis-Hastings算法对Metropolis算法进行推广，不再要求"
        ],
        "bbox": [
            84,
            320,
            895,
            527
        ],
        "page_idx": 13
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "建议分布对称，接收概率为 $r = \\frac{f(x^{*})}{f(x^{t - 1})} \\times \\frac{J(x^{t - 1} | x^{*})}{J(x^{*} | x^{t - 1})}$ 。",
        "bbox": [
            91,
            627,
            728,
            733
        ],
        "page_idx": 13
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "思考",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            142,
            196,
            237
        ],
        "page_idx": 14
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "1. 写出Metropolis-Hastings算法的转移函数 $T$ 。",
            "2. 根据以上证明思路证明: Metropolis-Hastings算法的转移函数 $T$ 满足平衡条件。"
        ],
        "bbox": [
            83,
            320,
            901,
            646
        ],
        "page_idx": 14
    }
]